375
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,169
What's the matter, Dongge?

376
00:23:58,169 --> 00:24:00,410
Do you feel ill?

377
00:24:00,410 --> 00:24:04,789
No. I feel dizzy all of a sudden.

378
00:24:04,789 --> 00:24:07,350
Shall I ask Mr. Shao to take you back?

379
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:10,509
No need. He's busy now.

380
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:14,679
Look. I'm getting better.

381
00:24:16,340 --> 00:24:18,160
