394
00:25:10,650 --> 00:25:14,309
I spent ten minutes checking it.

395
00:25:14,309 --> 00:25:15,860
I'll give you 30 minutes.

396
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:18,699
Be serious. As if you're taking the exam.

397
00:25:18,699 --> 00:25:20,000
Is it necessary?

398
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,640
Start.

399
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:36,510
