461
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:13,759
He knows nothing. Only you trust him. He can't be trusted.

462
00:31:13,759 --> 00:31:16,029
I'm afraid that the doctor at the hospital would say so as well.

463
00:31:16,029 --> 00:31:19,459
