474
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:46,400
That won't happen. That won't happen.

475
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,450
You were far apart from me back then.

476
00:31:49,450 --> 00:31:50,999
But I got you back in the end.

477
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:56,269
Even if you went to the king of Hell, I'd still bring you back.

478
00:31:57,470 --> 00:31:59,540
