00:34:35,605 --> 00:34:37,705
One hundred and six points.

528
00:34:43,555 --> 00:34:45,455
Dongge. Shao Hua.

529
00:34:45,455 --> 00:34:47,865
Where are you going?

530
00:34:47,865 --> 00:34:52,424
Dongge. Shao Hua. Let us accompany you both.

531
00:34:52,424 --> 00:34:53,434
I'll go as well.

532
00:34:53,435 --> 00:34:55,335
Me too.

533
00:34:57,845 --> 00:34:59,635
We'll accompany you to the hospital.

534
00:34:59,635 --> 00:35:01,085
Let's go.

535
00:35:03,785 --> 00:35:05,875
It's good to have you all.

536
00:35:06,785 --> 00:35:11,074
With all our support, nothing can really harm you.

537
00:35:13,435 --> 00:35:15,135
Okay.

538
00:35:15,135 --> 00:35:16,575
Let's go.

539
00:35:23,705 --> 00:35:25,605
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

