541
00:35:31,975 --> 00:35:33,675
Is the result out?

542
00:35:35,665 --> 00:35:37,699
What did the doctor say?

543
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:39,170
<i>[Consulting Room II]</i>

544
00:35:43,585 --> 00:35:46,095
What did the doctor say?

545
00:35:51,035 --> 00:35:52,935
I can bear it.

