00:36:20,305 --> 00:36:22,505
You're pregnant.

552
00:36:22,505 --> 00:36:24,985
- I...
- Mr. Shao.
- No wonder you felt dizzy and sick before.

553
00:36:24,985 --> 00:36:26,574
Congratulations!

554
00:36:26,574 --> 00:36:27,574
Bravo!

555
00:36:27,574 --> 00:36:28,844
Mr. Shao, you're old yet strong.

556
00:36:28,844 --> 00:36:30,954
You're pregnant!

557
00:36:30,954 --> 00:36:32,085
I was so scared.

558
00:36:32,085 --> 00:36:34,055
That's great.

559
00:36:38,265 --> 00:36:39,744
You have strong pregnancy symptoms.

560
00:36:39,745 --> 00:36:41,955
Yes.

561
00:36:41,955 --> 00:36:44,445
You're amazing.

562
00:36:44,445 --> 00:36:49,114
For this matter, almost half of the restoration division is gone.

563
00:36:52,375 --> 00:36:55,005
Well, young people these days.

564
00:36:55,005 --> 00:36:58,395
Master, it's a good thing.

565
00:36:58,395 --> 00:37:00,894
Madam Yu isn't young anymore. Right?

566
00:37:00,894 --> 00:37:03,844
It's good for them to help.

567
00:37:05,005 --> 00:37:07,584
Maybe I should go and give them a hand, too?

568
00:37:07,584 --> 00:37:11,464
Just do your work. Don't worry about others.

569
00:37:11,464 --> 00:37:14,155
You haven't sorted yourself out yet.

570
00:37:14,915 --> 00:37:16,455
There's nothing I need to sort out.

571
00:37:16,455 --> 00:37:19,184
Stop giving me random advice all the time.

572
00:37:19,184 --> 00:37:24,315
You're getting older all the time.

573
00:37:26,395 --> 00:37:29,335
I'm... I'm not in a hurry.

574
00:37:31,975 --> 00:37:34,575
I'll get going now.

575
00:37:34,575 --> 00:37:36,604
Are you not going to wait for Xue?

576
00:37:36,604 --> 00:37:38,194
I've got other plans.

577
00:37:38,194 --> 00:37:40,125
Zhang Qi!

578
00:37:41,045 --> 00:37:43,685
Why are you in such a hurry?

579
00:37:43,685 --> 00:37:46,350
He must have gone to the cybercafe.

580
00:37:47,105 --> 00:37:49,075
Sunian.

581
00:37:49,075 --> 00:37:50,455
What score did you get?

582
00:37:50,455 --> 00:37:52,875
How did you make it?

583
00:37:53,975 --> 00:37:57,104
<i>Thank you for helping me during weekends.</i>

584
00:37:57,104 --> 00:37:59,414
<i>These are the papers of Grade 10 students.</i>

585
00:37:59,414 --> 00:38:03,434
<i>I hope you can be responsible for both yourself and others.</i>

586
00:38:03,434 --> 00:38:06,304
<i>Mark the papers carefully. Go ahead.</i>

587
00:38:10,995 --> 00:38:15,224
<i>Sunian, normally, you don't like to get involved in this kind of thing. Right?</i>

588
00:38:15,224 --> 00:38:17,974
<i>Why did you take the initiative this time?</i>

589
00:38:18,915 --> 00:38:22,384
<i>It's not good to just study on my own all the time.</i>

590
00:38:23,130 --> 00:38:28,590
♫ <i>The time that we had lost</i> ♫

591
00:38:28,590 --> 00:38:32,220
<i>[Grade 10 Mathematics Paper]</i>
♫ <i>Slowly emerges from the sea</i> ♫

592
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:38,250
♫ <i> It turns out that the person who didn't go far is at hand</i> ♫

593
00:38:38,250 --> 00:38:41,269
♫ <i>Once you hesitated to bid farewell</i> ♫

594
00:38:41,269 --> 00:38:45,380
♫ <i>Staggering to take adventures</i> ♫

595
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:53,059
♫ <i>In different dreams Walking step by step</i> ♫

596
00:38:53,059 --> 00:38:56,794
<i>Mr. Zhang, I want to ask you a personal favor.</i>

597
00:38:56,794 --> 00:38:59,016
<i>Please consider it.</i>

598
00:38:59,016 --> 00:39:01,154
Sunian, thank you for saving my life.

599
00:39:01,154 --> 00:39:04,584
If something happens to you, I'll try my best to save you.

600
00:39:04,584 --> 00:39:07,774
I'm fine. You should study harder.

601
00:39:07,774 --> 00:39:10,174
<i>[Haircut, Perms, Hair Treatment]</i>

602
00:39:10,174 --> 00:39:11,905
- You know?
- Yes.

603
00:39:11,905 --> 00:39:13,245
Hello.

604
00:39:13,245 --> 00:39:15,104
Is class over?

605
00:39:15,105 --> 00:39:18,034
Xue, you came back just in time. Go back home quickly.

606
00:39:18,034 --> 00:39:19,894
There's good news for you.

607
00:39:19,894 --> 00:39:21,104
What is it?

608
00:39:21,104 --> 00:39:23,480
You're going to be a sister.

609
00:39:25,165 --> 00:39:28,444
There's an age gap of over ten years between them.

610
00:39:28,444 --> 00:39:30,285
Will they not get along well?

611
00:39:30,285 --> 00:39:31,405
Don't worry.

612
00:39:31,405 --> 00:39:33,894
They're siblings. It should be okay.

613
00:39:33,894 --> 00:39:35,665
Right?

614
00:39:35,665 --> 00:39:38,744
Will it be troublesome to give birth to the second child?

615
00:39:38,744 --> 00:39:40,134
I think it's fine.

616
00:39:40,134 --> 00:39:42,674
Both of them are the only child of their own family.

617
00:39:42,674 --> 00:39:44,105
Just a small fine will do.

618
00:39:44,105 --> 00:39:46,674
If they can't hand it in, I can help them.

619
00:39:46,674 --> 00:39:48,874
When the child is born, I'm going to be the godmother.

620
00:39:48,874 --> 00:39:51,354
You wish. I've booked it long ago. You are next in line.

621
00:39:51,354 --> 00:39:53,474
- So you wouldn't stand down.
- Exactly.

622
00:39:53,475 --> 00:39:56,504
All right. You come first. She comes next. And I come last. Is it okay?

623
00:39:56,504 --> 00:39:57,614
- Okay.
- All right.

624
00:39:57,614 --> 00:39:59,294
That settles it then.

625
00:39:59,294 --> 00:40:00,224
I'll head back and cook.

626
00:40:00,225 --> 00:40:01,624
- Okay, bye.
- Bye.

627
00:40:01,625 --> 00:40:02,664
Hurry up and go home.

628
00:40:02,665 --> 00:40:04,894
- Goodbye.
- Okay.

629
00:40:04,894 --> 00:40:06,885
Why are there only the two of you?

630
00:40:07,375 --> 00:40:10,744
Where's that little rebel? Isn't he with you?

631
00:40:12,515 --> 00:40:14,654
Did he go to the cybercafe again?

632
00:40:14,654 --> 00:40:16,875
That brat. I'm going to find him.

633
00:40:16,875 --> 00:40:19,434
This spoiled kid is always like this.

634
00:40:20,775 --> 00:40:22,945
Let's go back, too.

635
00:40:23,785 --> 00:40:27,254
Mom, you go back first.

636
00:40:27,254 --> 00:40:28,975
Okay.

637
00:40:49,355 --> 00:40:51,465
What's wrong?

638
00:40:51,465 --> 00:40:53,805
Nothing.

639
00:40:53,805 --> 00:40:56,065
I'm just...

640
00:40:57,225 --> 00:40:59,275
I'm just a little confused.

641
00:41:00,185 --> 00:41:02,705
You don't want a younger brother or sister?

642
00:41:04,145 --> 00:41:06,255
I don't know either.

643
00:41:10,875 --> 00:41:13,514
Let's go. I'll take you somewhere.

644
00:41:13,514 --> 00:41:15,505
Where are we going?

645
00:41:19,775 --> 00:41:22,964
Sunian, how did you discover this place?

646
00:41:22,964 --> 00:41:25,975
I didn't discover it. It was always here.

647
00:41:25,975 --> 00:41:28,804
That's how the back of the Forbidden City looks.

648
00:41:29,845 --> 00:41:32,704
Those who come here always leave from here.

649
00:41:32,704 --> 00:41:34,994
But few people look back.

650
00:41:34,995 --> 00:41:37,065
Sunian, you're awesome.

651
00:41:45,035 --> 00:41:46,715
Are you still worried?

652
00:41:48,665 --> 00:41:50,455
Yes.

653
00:41:52,625 --> 00:41:54,255
I'm all ears.

654
00:41:55,895 --> 00:42:00,085
I... I'm afraid you'll tease me.

655
00:42:00,085 --> 00:42:03,074
I always teased you.

656
00:42:05,195 --> 00:42:09,424
I'm worried if I do have a younger brother or sister,

657
